OL,3,C2024 set to be hottest year on record,
OL,4,Ccapping a 'decade of deadly heat'
OL,6,FThe past year is a set to be the
OL,7,Fhottest on record, capping a "decade
OL,8,Fof deadly heat", the UN has said.
OL,10,FIn his new year message, UN secretary-
OL,11,Fgeneral Antonio Guterres said the 10
OL,12,Fhottest years on record have happened
OL,13,Fin the last decade, including 2024.
OL,15,FThe UN's climate and weather agency,
OL,16,Fthe World Meteorological Organisation
OL,17,F(WMO), will publish official
OL,18,Ftemperature figures for the year in
OL,19,FJanuary.
