OL,3,C2024 set to be hottest year on record,
OL,4,Ccapping a 'decade of deadly heat'
OL,6,FRecord-breaking temperatures in 2024
OL,7,Ffollow a decade of unprecedented heat
OL,8,Ffuelled by human activities, and
OL,9,Fdriving increasing weather extremes.
OL,11,FGreenhouse gas levels continue to
OL,12,Freach new highs, locking in more heat
OL,13,Ffor the future, the agency warned.
OL,15,FMr Guterres said: "I can officially
OL,16,Freport that we have just endured a
OL,17,Fdecade of deadly heat.
OL,19,F"The top ten 10 hottest years on
OL,20,Frecord have happened in the last 10
OL,21,Fyears, including 2024.
