OL,3,C2024 set to be hottest year on record,
OL,4,Ccapping a 'decade of deadly heat'
OL,6,F"This year we saw record-breaking
OL,7,Frainfall and flooding events and
OL,8,Fterrible loss of life in so many
OL,9,Fcountries, causing heartbreak to
OL,10,Fcommunities on every continent," she
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"Tropical cyclones caused a terrible
OL,14,Fhuman and economic toll, most recently
OL,15,Fin the French overseas department of
OL,16,FMayotte in the Indian Ocean.
OL,18,F"Intense heat scorched dozens of
OL,19,Fcountries, with temperatures topping
OL,20,F50C on a number of occasions.
OL,21,FWildfires wreaked devastation."
