OL,6,FThe WMO warned that as global
OL,7,Ftemperatures rise and extreme heat
OL,8,Fevents worsen, there is a growing need
OL,9,Ffor countries and international
OL,10,Forganisations to work together to
OL,11,Ftackle severe heat risks.
